OL,3,C'Eating ice lollies should be part of
OL,4,Cprimary school curriculum'
OL,6,FPrimary school pupils should be given
OL,7,Fice lollies in science lessons to
OL,8,Fensure learning is grounded in
OL,9,Fengaging real-life experiences, a
OL,10,Fcoalition of scientific associations
OL,11,Fhas said.
OL,13,FA new primary science curriculum
OL,14,Fshould be introduced which offers
OL,15,F"essential experiences" in class so
OL,16,Fall children have opportunities to
OL,17,Frelate to scientific concepts,
OL,18,Faccording to a report.
