OL,6,FChildren with limited first-hand
OL,7,Fexperiences are "undeniably at a
OL,8,Fdisadvantage", the report suggested.
OL,10,FIt said: "This is a fundamental equity
OL,11,Fissue, and the provision of rich
OL,12,Fessential experiences for children
OL,13,F(particularly in the early and lower
OL,14,Fprimary years) will go some way in
OL,15,Faddressing this.
