OL,6,F"These concrete experiences form a
OL,7,Fbasis from which children can draw
OL,8,Fevidence for their ideas, making
OL,9,Fchildren ready for the more abstract
OL,10,Flearning they will encounter at
OL,11,Fsecondary school."
OL,13,FThe Government launched its curriculum
OL,14,Fand assessment review last month,
OL,15,Fwhich will be chaired by education
OL,16,Fexpert Professor Becky Francis.
