OL,3,C'Eating ice lollies should be part of
OL,4,Cprimary school curriculum'
OL,6,FAylin Ozkan, a teacher and education
OL,7,Fpolicy specialist at the Royal Society
OL,8,Fof Chemistry, said: "One of the
OL,9,Frecommendations for chemistry is that
OL,10,Fby the age of 11, all children should
OL,11,Fstart to understand how temperature
OL,12,Fworks and how heating and cooling can
OL,13,Fchange things.
OL,15,F"What better prop is there for a
OL,16,Fteacher to help explain this than an
OL,17,Fice lolly?
