OL,6,F"It's a cheap solution, and will allow
OL,7,Fchildren the opportunity to develop
OL,8,Ftheir scientific confidence whatever
OL,9,Ftheir background ` this is exactly
OL,10,Fwhat curriculum reform should be
OL,11,Faiming to do."
OL,13,FCharles Tracy, senior adviser in
OL,14,Flearning and skills at the Institute
OL,15,Fof Physics, said: "Many children enjoy
OL,16,Fmaking noise ` but harnessing this in
OL,17,Fthe classroom can help teach the
OL,18,Fbasics of concepts such as pitch and
OL,19,Fvolume".
